1
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:37,660
Pull this old woman out, drag her away and chop her up!

2
00:00:37,660 --> 00:00:39,660
Dump her at the gate of the Grand Tutor's mansion.

3
00:00:39,660 --> 00:00:40,860
Tell Grand Tutor Wei,

4
00:00:41,400 --> 00:00:44,800
if his dog of a servant dares to act wildly in front of me again,

5
00:00:45,030 --> 00:00:47,230
I will bring my sword to the court tomorrow

6
00:00:47,230 --> 00:00:48,200
and chop him up too.

7
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,160
General,

8
00:00:49,900 --> 00:00:51,300
Grand Tutor Wei is your future father-in-law.

9
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:52,730
Acting like this might...

10
00:00:52,730 --> 00:00:54,190
Bullshit father-in-law!

11
00:00:54,300 --> 00:00:56,360
If he pisses me off, I'll slash him...

12
00:01:22,930 --> 00:01:26,760
General, you have fought in bloody battles for years and killed enough.

13
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,600
There is no need to kill an evil servant

14
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:30,130
and add to your sins.

15
00:01:33,229 --> 00:01:34,030
Throw her out.

16
00:01:34,900 --> 00:01:35,759
Yes, General.

17
00:01:49,830 --> 00:01:51,500
Lu Jingxing, put me down.

18
00:01:51,500 --> 00:01:52,500
I can walk myself.

19
00:01:53,060 --> 00:01:54,990
You don't even have a pair of shoes.

20
00:01:55,259 --> 00:01:57,330
If the bricks and tiles on the ground cut your feet,

21
00:01:57,330 --> 00:01:59,700
and your blood stains my floor,

22
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,730
how do you plan to pay for it?

23
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:04,360
You...

24
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:30,460
In the past at the Minister's mansion,

25
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:32,930
the Eldest Miss managed the inner courtyard.

26
00:02:32,930 --> 00:02:36,360
You never showed mercy to an evil old dog like Nanny Zhang.

27
00:02:36,530 --> 00:02:38,030
Why are you so timid now?

28
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:41,230
You are not the horse slave you used to be.

29
00:02:41,230 --> 00:02:43,960
General Weibei is highly favored by the Emperor.

30
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:46,290
This marriage was granted by His Majesty.

31
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:48,460
If you kill people from the Grand Preceptor's mansion,

32
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:50,260
the censors will not let you off.

33
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:52,329
His Majesty will also suspect you.

34
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,360
I fought my way through mountains of corpses and seas of blood

35
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,690
to sit in this position,

36
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:00,800
just so I don't have to take the crap from those nobles.

37
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,430
Now I can kill whoever I want,

38
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:05,760
and marry whoever I want.

39
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:07,230
When the Emperor gets angry,

40
00:03:07,230 --> 00:03:08,560
my Shen family, who served as officials for three generations,

41
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,160
was overthrown overnight.

42
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:12,460
How long can your little military merit last?

43
00:03:12,460 --> 00:03:13,700
Lu Jingxing,

44
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,260
I advise you to watch your words and actions.

45
00:03:16,260 --> 00:03:17,860
Are you worried about me?

46
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:19,700
I wouldn't dare.

47
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:38,300
You know you are just a servant,

48
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,130
just a test-marriage maid.

49
00:03:40,530 --> 00:03:42,960
What right do you have to advise me to watch my words and actions?

50
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:45,490
Do you still think it's the past, Eldest Miss?

51
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:46,800
I wouldn't dare.

52
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,890
But since the General despises me so much,

53
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:52,000
why hurt someone for me?

54
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,560
I just couldn't stand that old dog

55
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,230
showing off on my turf.

56
00:03:55,230 --> 00:03:56,700
Who said it was for you?

57
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,220
It's best if it wasn't.

58
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,530
You...

59
00:04:05,300 --> 00:04:07,000
Put away your sharp tongue,

60
00:04:07,530 --> 00:04:08,660
and serve me well.

61
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,830
Maybe if I'm happy,

62
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:15,260
there will be a bite to eat for you in this mansion in the future.

63
00:04:16,730 --> 00:04:18,130
You are joking, General.

64
00:04:18,529 --> 00:04:20,190
I don't dare to expect so much.

65
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,730
I see the General is a bit fierce,

66
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:33,100
but he really likes you, Miss.

67
00:04:34,530 --> 00:04:36,600
Why don't you be softer,

68
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,130
beg the General

69
00:04:38,130 --> 00:04:39,700
to keep you here.

70
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,000
Maybe you can become a concubine in the future,

71
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,760
and have someone to rely on for the rest of your life.

72
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:47,130
We are all servants of the Grand Preceptor's mansion.

73
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:48,730
How can we betray our master?

74
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:50,730
Once we complete our master's orders,

75
00:04:50,730 --> 00:04:52,330
we naturally have to go back.

76
00:04:52,330 --> 00:04:53,790
Then on this second night,

77
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:55,860
you must serve the General well.

78
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:59,190
It will be easier to report back when we return in three days.

79
00:04:59,330 --> 00:05:01,360
I have to serve him tonight.

80
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,800
Yes, not just tonight.

81
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:06,060
You have to serve him tomorrow night too.

82
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,860
Damn it.

83
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:12,430
Everything is arranged at the death row.

84
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:14,500
Minister Shen's shackles have been quietly removed.

85
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:17,600
And the best military doctor was sent to treat his wounds.

86
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,400
General, forgive me for talking too much.

87
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:20,900
I've really never seen anyone take revenge

88
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:22,230
on an enemy like this.

89
00:05:22,230 --> 00:05:24,860
Hmph, I just want everyone in the Minister's mansion

90
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:26,160
to receive my favor

91
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:28,900
so they will be ashamed and regret it for the rest of their lives.

92
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:30,560
This is the cruelest revenge.

93
00:05:31,860 --> 00:05:32,930
In my opinion,

94
00:05:32,930 --> 00:05:35,430
the eldest Miss Shen has you completely wrapped around her finger.

95
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:36,730
General, how is this revenge?

96
00:05:36,730 --> 00:05:37,300
It's clearly...

97
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:37,930
Shut up!

98
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:40,830
Just watch.

99
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:42,100
When Shen Luyi comes to me,

100
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:43,630
I will torture her to death.

101
00:05:43,630 --> 00:05:44,860
Your servant, Shen Luyi,

102
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:46,460
requests to see the General.

103
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:50,760
Come in.
